title: Ihor Tyshchenko
text:
Ihor Tyschenko (; born 11 May 1989) is a <a href="professional">professional</a> <a href="Ukraine">Ukrainian</a> <a href="Association%20football">football</a> <a href="midfielder">midfielder</a> who plays for <a href="FC%20Yarud%20Mariupol">Yarud Mariupol</a>.
Born in Vladivostok, in the <a href="Russian%20Far%20East">Russian Far East</a>, since 1994 Tyshchenko lived in Mariupol when he was five.
Career.
On 25 February 2016, he signed a half year contract with <a href="Poland">Polish</a> team <a href="%C5%9Al%C4%85sk%20Wroc%C5%82aw">Śląsk Wrocław</a>.
